cc:Work.dc:title: Elvie #018
cc:Work.dc:description:
[Panel 1: Evie and her friend are standing by an open refrigerator. Elvie is pouring a drink from a blender in the fridge.]
Elvie: I've bought an Ubuntu-powered fridge.
It can talk to my Ubuntu phone, and I've hacked a smoothie maker into it via the internal USB ports.
[Panel 2: Elvie's friend is holding the drink, and has spat a large amount out, all over Elvie.]
Elvie: I guess aubergine and orange isn't to everyone's taste.
